  "dailyGraceReflectionLabel": "WALAACA HABEEN",
  "dailyGraceCopiedToast": "Ayah koobeyay clipboard-ka",

  "dailyScripture0Text": "Reer xaq-basta waxay jirtaan hadii iyo webiyaal, meesha sharaf leh marka caasimada adag.",
  "dailyScripture0Ref": "Qur'aan 54:54-55",
  "dailyScripture1Text": "Iyo ma anuuba soo dirney adiga illaa ahayd naxariista aalmaha.",
  "dailyScripture1Ref": "Qur'aan 21:107",
  "dailyScripture2Text": "Mise Allah kuma tafsii adeega isaga? Laakiin waxay cabsi kaa geystaan kuwa kale maga.",
  "dailyScripture2Ref": "Qur'aan 39:36",
  "dailyScripture3Text": "Laxan waxaad iska qabashid waxa waxay wanaag lagu tahay; iyo laxan waxaad jeceshid waxa waxay dib u tahay. Allah wuxuu yaqaan, adina ma aad taqaanin.",
  "dailyScripture3Ref": "Qur'aan 2:216",
  "dailyScripture4Text": "Dhanto Allah wuxuu jira kuwa sabura.",
  "dailyScripture4Ref": "Qur'aan 2:153",
  "dailyScripture5Text": "Oo sidaas aah xusuuso aan, xusuusan. Iyo mahadsana iyo naa shukayn.",
  "dailyScripture5Ref": "Qur'aan 2:152",
  "dailyScripture6Text": "Dhanto caasimada aad u wanaagsan ee marka Allah waxay tahay kuwa xaq basta ugu aad.",
  "dailyScripture6Ref": "Qur'aan 49:13",
  "dailyScripture7Text": "Iyo Xaakimkaagu waxuu amray inaadna ibadine jidhka iska sii gee oo ay aad xaram u ahaa iyo waalidyadaa.",
  "dailyScripture7Ref": "Qur'aan 17:23",
  "dailyScripture8Text": "Dhanto, dhaawacda walaagu waxaa ku jira nabadi.",
  "dailyScripture8Ref": "Qur'aan 94:6",
  "dailyScripture9Text": "Iyo isna waa jira halka aad joogtaan. Iyo Allah waxuu iska yaqaan qofka aad sameen.",
  "dailyScripture9Ref": "Qur'aan 57:4",
  "dailyScripture10Text": "Allah waxuu af-wayn kaato naf illaa waxa ay karti tahay.",
  "dailyScripture10Ref": "Qur'aan 2:286",
  "dailyScripture11Text": "Iyo kuwa isna isku duwiya Allah — sidaas isna iska tafsii.",
  "dailyScripture11Ref": "Qur'aan 65:3",
  "dailyScripture12Text": "Naxariistayga waxay goystaa wax walba.",
  "dailyScripture12Ref": "Qur'aan 7:156",
  "dailyScripture13Text": "Iyo marka abdaaladaygu kugu weydiiyaan af - dhanto anigu waan jira. Waxaan jawaban qofka yedha markuu yedaayo.",
  "dailyScripture13Ref": "Qur'aan 2:186",
  "dailyScripture14Text": "Kuwa wax xaq ah samaynaa, ama lab ama gabar, oo leh imaan - waxaan si xiniyo ah lagaa nooleeye.",
  "dailyScripture14Ref": "Qur'aan 16:97",
  "dailyScripture15Text": "Dhanto, Allah wuxuu ma beddeli doono noola qof, illaa ay beddelen wax jira iyada.",
  "dailyScripture15Ref": "Qur'aan 13:11",
  "dailyScripture16Text": "Oo aan laayo iyo aan murugo, iyo aad tahay layaab haddii aad yihiin uu imaan jira.",
  "dailyScripture16Ref": "Qur'aan 3:139",
  "dailyScripture17Text": "Yaa adeegayga oo dhan magaar ka yimid, ha niyad xumeeye naxariista Allah. Dhanto, Allah wuu cafiyi karaa dhambi walba.",
  "dailyScripture17Ref": "Qur'aan 39:53",
  "dailyScripture18Text": "Iyo kuwa ka ayaanta Allah - isna hadii sabiisa, iyo isna si uu geeya waxa uu filayn.",
  "dailyScripture18Ref": "Qur'aan 65:2-3",
  "dailyScripture19Text": "Ha niyad xumeeyne naxariista Allah.",
  "dailyScripture19Ref": "Qur'aan 12:87",
  "dailyScripture20Text": "Iyo dhanto, Qur'aanka wuu sahansah jirin si loo xusuusto. Sidaas miyaa mid yedha?",
  "dailyScripture20Ref": "Qur'aan 54:17",
  "dailyScripture21Text": "Iyo Xaakimkaa waxa uu kuu helay ilmo iyo waxa uu kuu hagaajiyay.",
  "dailyScripture21Ref": "Qur'aan 93:7",
  "dailyScripture22Text": "Iyo Xaakimkaagu wuxuu leeyahay: I yedha; waxaan jawaban doonaa.",
  "dailyScripture22Ref": "Qur'aan 40:60",
  "dailyScripture23Text": "Iyo dhanto, waxaan si caasimad ah u sharaf siinay gabar Adam.",
  "dailyScripture23Ref": "Qur'aan 17:70",
  "dailyScripture24Text": "Iyo raadso caalaamo dhexdhexaada iyo salah.",
  "dailyScripture24Ref": "Qur'aan 2:45",
  "dailyScripture25Text": "Kuwa kuwa wax culuq ah samaynaa sidaa ay wax culuq ah iska yeelan.",
  "dailyScripture25Ref": "Qur'aan 99:7",
  "dailyScripture26Text": "Si aan waxba la taaban, caalaamo Allah waa u dhow.",
  "dailyScripture26Ref": "Qur'aan 2:214",
  "dailyScripture27Text": "Iyo kuwa mahadsada - mahadsadis waxay u tahay naf isaga.",
  "dailyScripture27Ref": "Qur'aan 31:12",

  "dailyReflection0": "Maalinta hadda ee dhamaatay, is fiiri albaab mid oo naxariista Allah ay muuqday.",
  "dailyReflection1": "Geyd hore Allah waxa ay kaa caleen maalinta.",
  "dailyReflection2": "Odhan sahib mid oo maalinta iyo sheekaha mahadsana Allah.",
  "dailyReflection3": "Oday nabad ku axada kaydka Allah.",
  "dailyReflection4": "Fiiro halka aad u yedhay inaad caalaami garad iyo xusun samaasid maalinta.",
  "dailyReflection5": "Tag waxa aad kari kaarto iyo isku duwi nidaam Allah.",
  "dailyReflection6": "Markii uu dhammaatay maalinta, qaad caalaami nabad dhikrka Allah.",
  "dailyReflection7": "Fiiro sida aad u khadartay salado iyo sheekaha mahadsana Allah.",
  "dailyReflection8": "Walaac waxa aad dhegeysta sabuur maalinta iyo garashadda.",
  "dailyReflection9": "Raadi caafimad dhibaatada maalinta - naxariista Allah waa ay balballan.",
  "dailyReflection10": "Odhan hadii caalaami samaasid iyo du'a iyaga.",
  "dailyReflection11": "Joog oo mahadsana: maxaa adeegyaagu siiyey maalinta oo aad wayd wayn?",
  "dailyReflection12": "Walaac ayah Qur'aanka oo ku saabsan meeshaa aad jirta hadda.",
  "dailyReflection13": "Fiiro sidee aad isticmaalay waqtigaada maalinta - iyo gayd buuxa Allah.",
  "dailyReflection14": "Oday caalaami markii habeen ay dhacdo, dhanto Allah waxa uu jira adigaa.",
  "dailyReflection15": "Fiiro hadii wax mid aad adeega qoysadda iyo bulshada maalinta.",
  "dailyReflection16": "Markii habeen ay dhacdo, samaad Tawbah - Allah wuu jeceshahay kuwa dib u celiya.",
  "dailyReflection17": "Walaac gacan Allah sajaday maalinta, haddii ay aad yar tahay.",
  "dailyReflection18": "Fiiro waxa aad barsatay maalinta iyo sidee ay kaa dhow geysay Allah.",
  "dailyReflection19": "Tag dhalaalen maalinta-Allah waxuu qaato waxa aad karti karto.",
  "dailyReflection20": "Fiiro malaaca maalinta ee aad yidi kartay hagga hagga, iyo bar.",
  "dailyReflection21": "Samaad du'a kuwa dhibanaya - du'adu wax cusub ayay u tahay.",
  "dailyReflection22": "Xusuusto shukuur aad caadi u mooddo iyo sheekaha mahadsana Allah.",
  "dailyReflection23": "Walaac niyad maalinta - marke niyadu ahayd Allah? Buuxa markale.",
  "dailyReflection24": "Markii habeen ay caalaami joogto, dhegeyso yakiin Allah caalaami.",
  "dailyReflection25": "Fiiro meeshaa aad helasid xooga maalinta - xoogaasi waa ka yimid Allah.",
  "dailyReflection26": "Odhan wax mid aad samayn doonto buuxa oo aad waydiin samaasid.",
  "dailyReflection27": "Markii aad diyaar u tahay oday, geyd nafkaaga Allah - isna waa hagga kale.",

